10:55.328 --> 11:01.778
I'll be sharing today from the parable of the seed in Matthew chapter 13, verses 24 through 30.

11:03.170 --> 11:07.274
Matthew chapter 14 verses 24 through 30.

11:12.339 --> 11:16.182
Now this is not the parable that's normally called the parable of the seeds.

11:17.504 --> 11:22.829
The parable of the seeds that we hear more about is actually the parable of the soils.

