11:47.402 --> 11:50.125
One was sown on rocky soil.

11:51.046 --> 11:55.131
So because the soil was too rocky, the bird came and snatched it up.

11:55.251 --> 11:58.054
So that seed got snatched so it didn't do what it was supposed to do.

11:58.775 --> 12:01.298
And then there was one seed that was sown

12:01.506 --> 12:05.252
